Thin targets containing about 1 mg/cm**2 of target
material. The target sandwich containing the sample and
two thin monitor copper foils were fixed in the
cyclotron probe and exposed to the external beam.
Enriched isotopes obtained from the Oak Ridge, either
in elementary or compound form were used as targets.
